fast, 5 min max)\nDo a quick web search for 1-2 recent papers relevant to Compositional Cognition:\n- causal discovery OR causal reasoning OR causal inference\n- mixture of experts OR sparse models OR MoE\n- episodic memory OR memory architecture\n- synthetic cognition OR autonomous agents\n\nIf you find a paper directly relevant to the current research direction, add a brief note to sandbox/research/arxiv-relevance.md (title, URL, 1-sentence why relevant). If nothing relevant, skip silently.\n\n## After\nCommit your research changes to the sandbox git repo.\n\nReport: what did you do, what did you learn, what's the next experiment?","timeoutSeconds":900},"delivery":{"mode":"none","channel":"telegram","to":"8371302588"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774382493400,"lastRunAtMs":1774375959643,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":285995,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"lastDelivered":false},"deleteAfterRun":false}],"total":5,"offset":0,"limit":5,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774380495481}}
